47 template <typename T> class handle_traits {};
48 
62 template <typename T, typename traits=handle_traits<T>> class handle {
63 private:
64  static mkldnn_status_t dummy_destructor(T){ return mkldnn_success; }
65 
66  std::shared_ptr<typename std::remove_pointer<T>::type> _data;
67  handle(const handle &&) = delete;
68  handle &operator=(const handle &&other) = delete;
69 protected:
70  bool operator==(const T other) const { return other == _data.get(); }
71  bool operator!=(const T other) const { return !(*this == other); }
72 public:
76  handle(T t = 0, bool weak = false): _data(0) {
77  reset(t, weak);
78  }
79 
80  handle(const handle &other): _data(other._data) {}
81  handle &operator=(const handle &other) {
82  _data = other._data;
83  return *this;
84  }
88  void reset(T t, bool weak = false) {
89  _data.reset(t, weak ? &dummy_destructor : traits::destructor);
90  }
91 
93  T get() const { return _data.get(); }
94 
95  bool operator==(const handle &other) const { return other._data.get() == _data.get(); }
96  bool operator!=(const handle &other) const { return !(*this == other); }
97 };

450  void get_output_scales(int &mask, std::vector<float> &scales) const
451  {
452  mkldnn_dim_t count;
453  int c_mask;
454  const float *c_scales;
455  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_primitive_attr_get_output_scales(get(),
456  &count, &c_mask, &c_scales),
457  "could not get int output scales");
458  scales.resize(count);
459 
460  mask = c_mask;
461  for (mkldnn_dim_t c = 0; c < count; ++c)
462  scales[c] = c_scales[c];
463  }

997  struct desc {
998  friend struct memory;
1000  mkldnn_memory_desc_t data;
1001 
1003  desc(): data() {}
1004 
1010  desc(const dims &adims, data_type adata_type,
1011  format_tag aformat) {
1012  validate_dims(adims);
1013  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_desc_init_by_tag(&data, (int)adims.size(),
1014  adims.size() == 0 ? nullptr : &adims[0],
1015  convert_to_c(adata_type), convert_to_c(aformat)),
1016  "could not initialize a memory descriptor");
1017  }
1018 
1022  desc(const mkldnn_memory_desc_t &adata): data(adata) {}
1023 
1025  //
1028  desc submemory_desc(const dims &adims, const dims &offsets) {
1029  mkldnn_memory_desc_t sub_md;
1030  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_desc_init_submemory(&sub_md,
1031  &data, &adims[0], &offsets[0]),
1032  "could not initialize a sub-memory");
1033  return desc(sub_md);
1034  }
1035 
1038  size_t get_size() const { return mkldnn_memory_desc_get_size(&data); }
1039 
1040  bool operator==(const desc &other) const {
1041  return mkldnn_memory_desc_equal(&data, &other.data) != 0;
1042  }
1043 
1044  bool operator!=(const desc &other) const { return !operator==(other); }
1045  };
1046 
1052  memory(const desc &md, const engine &aengine, void *ahandle) {
1053  mkldnn_memory_t result;
1054  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_create(&result, &md.data,
1055  aengine.get(), ahandle), "could not create a memory");
1056  reset(result);
1057  }
1058 
1063  memory(const desc &md, const engine &aengine)
1064  : memory(md, aengine, MKLDNN_MEMORY_ALLOCATE) {}
1065 
1067  desc get_desc() const {
1068  const mkldnn_memory_desc_t *cdesc;
1069  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_get_memory_desc(get(), &cdesc),
1070  "could not get memory descriptor from a memory");
1071  return desc(*cdesc);
1072  }
1073 
1075  engine get_engine() const {
1076  mkldnn_engine_t engine_q;
1077  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_get_engine(get(), &engine_q),
1078  "could not get engine from a memory");
1079  return engine(engine_q);
1080  }
1081 
1085  void *get_data_handle() const {
1086  void *handle;
1087  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_memory_get_data_handle(get(), &handle),
1088  "could not get native handle");

1090  }

1094  "could not set native handle");
1095  }

1180 struct reorder : public primitive {

1182  primitive_desc(const engine &src_engine, const memory::desc &src_md,
1183  const engine &dst_engine, const memory::desc &dst_md,

1187  &src_md.data, src_engine.get(),

1189  "could not create a reorder primitive descriptor");

1191  }

1193  primitive_desc(const memory &src, const memory &dst,
1194  const primitive_attr &aattr = primitive_attr()) {
1195  mkldnn_primitive_desc_t result;
1196  auto src_md = src.get_desc();
1197  auto dst_md = dst.get_desc();
1198  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_reorder_primitive_desc_create(&result,
1199  &src_md.data, src.get_engine().get(),
1200  &dst_md.data, dst.get_engine().get(), aattr.get()),
1201  "could not create a reorder primitive descriptor");
1202  reset(result);
1203  }

1392 struct primitive_desc : public handle<mkldnn_primitive_desc_t> {
1393  primitive_desc(const_mkldnn_op_desc_t desc, const primitive_attr *attr,
1394  const engine &e, const_mkldnn_primitive_desc_t hint_fwd_pd) {
1395  mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_t iterator = nullptr;
1396  mkldnn_status_t status = mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_create(
1397  &iterator, desc, attr ? attr->get() : nullptr, e.get(),
1398  hint_fwd_pd);
1399  error::wrap_c_api(status,
1400  "could not create a primitive descriptor iterator");
1401  pd_iterator.reset(iterator);
1402  fetch_impl();
1403  }
1404 
1405  engine get_engine() { return engine::query(*this); }
1406 
1407  primitive_attr get_primitive_attr() const {
1408  const_mkldnn_primitive_attr_t const_cattr;
1409  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_primitive_desc_get_attr(get(), &const_cattr),
1410  "could not get attributes");
1411  mkldnn_primitive_attr_t cattr;
1412  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_primitive_attr_clone(&cattr, const_cattr),
1413  "could not clone attributes");
1414 
1415  primitive_attr attr;
1416  attr.reset(cattr);
1417  return attr;
1418  }
1419 
1421  const char *impl_info_str() const {
1422  const char *res;
1423  error::wrap_c_api(mkldnn_primitive_desc_query(get(),
1424  mkldnn_query_impl_info_str, 0, &res),
1425  "could not query implementation info string");
1426  return res;
1427  }
1428 
1430  memory::dim query_s64(query q) const {
1431  memory::dim res;
1432  mkldnn_status_t status = mkldnn_primitive_desc_query(get(),
1433  mkldnn::convert_to_c(q), 0, &res);
1434  return status == mkldnn_success ? res : 0;
1435  }
1436 
1443  bool next_impl() {
1444  mkldnn_status_t status = mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_next(
1445  pd_iterator.get());
1446  if (status == mkldnn_iterator_ends) return false;
1447  error::wrap_c_api(status, "primitive descriptor iterator next failed");
1448 
1449  fetch_impl();
1450  return true;
1451  }
1452 
1454  memory::desc query_md(query what, int idx = 0) const {
1455  std::vector<query> valid_q{ query::src_md, query::diff_src_md,
1456  query::weights_md, query::diff_weights_md, query::dst_md,
1457  query::diff_dst_md, query::workspace_md, query::scratchpad_md };
1458  if (!std::any_of(valid_q.cbegin(), valid_q.cend(),
1459  [=](query q) { return what == q; }))
1460  throw error(mkldnn_invalid_arguments, "invalid memory query");
1461 
1462  const mkldnn_memory_desc_t *cdesc = mkldnn_primitive_desc_query_md(
1463  get(), mkldnn::convert_to_c(what), idx);
1464  if (cdesc == nullptr) return memory::desc();
1465 
1466  return memory::desc(*cdesc);
1467  }
1468 
1469  // register specialized queries, e.g. src_desc()
1470 # define REG_QUERY_MD(name, what, idx) \
1471  memory::desc name ## _desc() const { return query_md(query::what ## _md, idx); }
1472 
1473  private:
1474  handle<mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_t> pd_iterator;
1475  void fetch_impl() {
1476  mkldnn_primitive_desc_t pd = mkldnn_primitive_desc_iterator_fetch(
1477  pd_iterator.get());
1478  error::wrap_c_api(pd != nullptr ? mkldnn_success : mkldnn_runtime_error,
1479  "could not fetch a primitive descriptor from the iterator");
1480  reset(pd);
1481  }
1482 };
